being grilled.

299
00:14:26,820 --> 00:14:28,410
Come on, where you gonna go?

300
00:14:28,452 --> 00:14:32,092
Your house burned down,
your wife's dead.
Business was sold off.

301
00:14:32,176 --> 00:14:36,109
The only thing you have left
is down the hall,
heading for a liver biopsy.

302
00:14:37,741 --> 00:14:42,971
Used to be this little
hole in the wall
run by a guy named Giancarlo.

303
00:14:44,017 --> 00:14:45,900
Made the best hoagies
in the world.

304
00:14:45,983 --> 00:14:49,121
Real Italian rolls,
prosciutto, provolone...

305
00:14:49,289 --> 00:14:50,586
(EXCLAIMS)

306
00:14:51,841 --> 00:14:53,891
How far is Atlantic City
from here?

307
00:14:54,059 --> 00:14:57,322
You have one day to live,
and you want a sandwich?

308
00:14:57,406 --> 00:14:59,247
People on death row
get a last meal.

309
00:14:59,372 --> 00:15:02,427
The state provides it.
Who's providing for you?

310
00:15:03,891 --> 00:15:05,481
You got a car? Money?

311
