to control the weather,

317
00:15:32,845 --> 00:15:34,854
but I'd prefer it
if you didn't eat in the car,

318
00:15:34,979 --> 00:15:36,318
I just had it detailed.

319
00:15:36,402 --> 00:15:38,033
I drive.
Oh, the hell he does.

320
00:15:38,117 --> 00:15:39,205
Sure.

321
00:15:40,126 --> 00:15:42,845
Aside from the fact
he just woke up
from a vegetative state,

322
00:15:42,971 --> 00:15:43,975
the guy doesn't
have a license.

323
00:15:44,059 --> 00:15:46,695
How about this?
Cops stop us, we lie.

324
00:15:46,820 --> 00:15:49,080
You know how to do that.
Chips.

325
00:15:52,176 --> 00:15:53,808
It's all the drugs
pumping through his system.

326
00:15:53,891 --> 00:15:56,527
Right now his reflexes
are better
than Dale Earnhardt Jr's.

327
00:15:56,611 --> 00:15:58,954
What's this? It says ipod.

328
00:16:02,050 --> 00:16:03,557
I'm coming.

329
00:16:10,167 --> 00:16:12,762
HOUSE: So let's talk about
toxic exposure.

330
00:16:17,448 --> 00:16:20,753
What was wrong
with the old colors?
I trusted brown.

331
00:16:21,464 --> 00:16:23,264
Do the purple ones
have chocolate inside?

332
00:16:23,305 --> 00:16:24,728
Raspberry cocaine.

333
00:16:25,398 --> 00:16:27,657
This house that burned down,
where was it?

334
00:16:27,699 --> 00:16:28,912
Moorestown, New Jersey.

335
00:16:28,954 --> 00:16:32,720
Listen, I really need to know
about the candy because
I'm allergic to berries.

336
00:16:32,720 --> 00:16:33,724
You didn't mention that.

337
00:16:33,766 --> 00:16:35,021
Is it significant?

338
00:16:35,105 --> 00:16:37,448
No. So where else
did you live?

339
00:16:37,531 --> 00:16:39,372
List everywhere,
including vacations,

340
00:16:39,456 --> 00:16:41,046
start with
when your wife got pregnant.

341
00:16:41,130 --> 00:16:44,561
We lived in Jersey.
Then we moved to Jersey,
from there, Jersey.

342
00:16:44,603 --> 00:16:47,573
What are you waiting to hear?
About the little cottage
in the Amazon

343
00:16:47,657 --> 00:16:49,749
with the mosquitoes
and the lead paint
all over the walls?

344
00:16:49,874 --> 00:16:50,837
Yes.

345
00:16:51,674 --> 00:16:52,552
You know what?

346
00:16:52,636 --> 00:16:56,611
