so you could suck all the fun
out of my one day of life.

347
00:16:56,695 --> 00:16:59,874
Well, you're outta luck,
because
that's totally why I'm here.

348
00:17:01,674 --> 00:17:03,640
Okay, rule change.

349
00:17:04,812 --> 00:17:07,071
Person with the money
makes the rules.
Or in this case,

350
00:17:07,113 --> 00:17:10,377
the person who's friends
with the person with the money
makes the rules.

351
00:17:10,502 --> 00:17:13,013
Well, you want answers
more than I want money.

352
00:17:13,264 --> 00:17:15,105
All right, so here's the game.

353
00:17:15,523 --> 00:17:16,695
Ask whatever you want.

354
00:17:16,778 --> 00:17:20,209
But for every question
I answer,
you have to answer one first.

355
00:17:20,251 --> 00:17:22,427
Why would you care
about anything I have to say?

356
00:17:22,469 --> 00:17:25,607
The day before I died,
I was a successful man.

357
00:17:26,234 --> 00:17:29,540
I had a factory
with over 200 employees.

358
00:17:29,582 --> 00:17:31,423
People listened when I talked.

359
00:17:31,799 --> 00:17:33,682
I liked power.

360
00:17:35,398 --> 00:17:39,958
Now, the only power
I have left
is the power to annoy you.

361
00:17:46,653 --> 00:17:48,745
I took Wilson's assistant
for coffee.

362
00:17:48,828 --> 00:17:51,213
Why?
Something Tritter said.

363
00:17:51,255 --> 00:17:52,510
She told me the police think

364
00:17:52,594 --> 00:17:56,109
