Do you?
Well, absolutely I do.

367
00:18:01,883 --> 00:18:03,473
I'm just checking
how naive you are.

368
00:18:03,557 --> 00:18:06,025
He's not gonna
steal his best friend's pad,
jeopardize his career.

369
00:18:06,067 --> 00:18:08,075
