localized response.

374
00:18:20,084 --> 00:18:23,138
I'll call House,
tell him we're gonna need
an answer soon.

375
00:18:25,439 --> 00:18:27,699
Get in your right lane
for 295.

376
00:18:28,368 --> 00:18:30,042
And pass me the Twizzlers.

377
00:18:33,975 --> 00:18:35,649
I'm curious...
No, you're not.

378
00:18:35,732 --> 00:18:37,239
Why would
a man's first instinct

379
00:18:37,322 --> 00:18:39,289
