478
00:23:23,264 --> 00:23:24,728
WILSON: I understand
he's a French chef

479
00:23:24,770 --> 00:23:26,653
but I'm sure
he can handle this.

480
00:23:26,695 --> 00:23:28,536
You need a 12-inch
Italian roll,

481
00:23:28,619 --> 00:23:32,720
oregano vinegar,
no, not balsamic vinegar,
oregano vinegar.

482
00:23:33,515 --> 00:23:35,732
Quid pro quo, Clarice.

483
00:23:36,276 --> 00:23:37,531
Game's still on.

484
00:23:37,573 --> 00:23:39,749
I thought the answer
was mercury poisoning.

485
00:23:39,833 --> 00:23:41,757
What other questions
would you care about?

486
00:23:41,883 --> 00:23:42,971
If you each had
one day to live,

