507
00:24:32,636 --> 00:24:35,983
You ask the questions,
answer them
and make tasty snacks.

508
00:24:36,611 --> 00:24:38,494
Let's go try the casino.

509
00:24:38,577 --> 00:24:40,418
And one day
our friendship will break

510
00:24:40,460 --> 00:24:43,724
