your theory that relationships
are conditional

511
00:24:43,766 --> 00:24:46,318
and you don't need
human connection
or deserve it,

512
00:24:46,444 --> 00:24:49,540
or whatever goes on
in that
rat-maze of your brain.

513
00:24:49,665 --> 00:24:51,590
Sorry, if I'd known
he was gonna be this annoying,

514
00:24:51,716 --> 00:24:53,347
