House's House of Whining,
state your complaint.

518
00:25:01,255 --> 00:25:02,762
The patient's BP
just dropped like a stone.

519
00:25:02,803 --> 00:25:03,808
<i>Do an echo.</i>

520
00:25:03,891 --> 00:25:05,272
Mercury isn't likely
to damage the...

