522
00:25:06,402 --> 00:25:08,410
Mercury test was negative.

523
00:25:10,084 --> 00:25:11,423
Do an echo.

524
00:25:17,573 --> 00:25:20,335
I was wrong.
Your son's still dying.

525
00:25:20,879 --> 00:25:23,724
I need to go over
every relative
you ever had. Again.

526
00:25:23,766 --> 00:25:26,904
And this time,
forget their diseases,
just tell me how they died.

527
00:25:27,029 --> 00:25:28,954
And we don't have time
to take turns.

528
00:25:28,996 --> 00:25:31,130
You give me the answers,
you get a big one at the end.

529
00:25:31,213 --> 00:25:32,594
You can go
for whatever you want.

530
00:25:32,678 --> 00:25:35,063
Destroy my privacy,
my dignity.

531
00:25:42,050 --> 00:25:43,431
Your grandmother?

532
00:25:43,473 --> 00:25:45,565
Heat exhaustion,
Fourth of July picnic.

533
00:25:45,607 --> 00:25:47,071
The woman was 92.

534
00:25:47,155 --> 00:25:49,331
Does anyone in the kitchen
know the hoagie shop

535
00:25:49,456 --> 00:25:51,130
that used to be
on St. James Place?

536
00:25:51,213 --> 00:25:53,347
You sister-in-law
with the diabetes.

537
00:25:53,473 --> 00:25:55,314
As far as you know,
is she still alive?
She's not.

538
00:25:55,356 --> 00:25:56,444
She was killed
in a traffic accident

539
00:25:56,527 --> 00:25:58,033
