from a Phillies game.

540
00:25:58,159 --> 00:25:59,623
I'm sure a lot of beer
was consumed.

541
00:25:59,707 --> 00:26:01,506
The Phillies lost.
Your father?

542
00:26:01,506 --> 00:26:03,640
Old age.
Heart finally gave out.

543
00:26:04,059 --> 00:26:05,021
Your wife's father?

544
00:26:05,063 --> 00:26:07,573
Hit-and-run,
walking the incontinent dog.

545
00:26:08,410 --> 00:26:10,335
Hi, do you guys deliver?

546
00:26:11,799 --> 00:26:12,762
Let me put it this way,

547
00:26:12,845 --> 00:26:15,774
